### 菜单管理接口

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### 创建菜单
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menuName": "测试菜单",
  "menuCode": "test_menu",
  "parentId": null,
  "menuType": "menu",
  "path": "/test",
  "icon": "test-icon",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "status": 1
}

### 更新菜单
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "menuName": "更新后的菜单名",
  "path": "/updated",
  "status": 1
}

### 删除菜单
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 根据ID查询菜单
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取菜单树
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu/tree
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取菜单列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/menu/list
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

